sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant QP as Knative Queue-Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP | 8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC localhost
    participant GPU as GPU / Model Weights

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012, mTLS STRICT<br/>Auth: Istio Service Identity
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>No encryption (pod-local)<br/>No auth
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC inference call<br/>localhost:8033<br/>No encryption, No auth
    TGIS->>GPU: Load model / run inference<br/>In-memory
    GPU-->>TGIS: Inference result
    TGIS-->>Caikit: gRPC response
    Caikit-->>QP: HTTP 200 JSON response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>IstioGW: gRPC caikit.runtime.Nlp<br/>HTTPS (h2)/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    IstioGW->>QP: gRPC forward<br/>8012/TCP, mTLS STRICT<br/>Auth: Istio Service Identity
    QP->>Caikit: gRPC (h2c)/8085<br/>No encryption (pod-local)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC inference call<br/>localhost:8033
    TGIS->>GPU: Run inference
    GPU-->>TGIS: Result
    TGIS-->>Caikit: gRPC response
    Caikit-->>QP: gRPC response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Response (mTLS)
    IstioGW-->>Client: gRPC response (TLS)

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>User Workload Monitoring

    Prom->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS<br/>NetworkPolicy allows from<br/>openshift-user-workload-monitoring
    Caikit-->>Prom: Metrics response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 4: Model Loading (Init)

    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    S3-->>Caikit: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model to /mnt/models<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / AccessKey
    Caikit->>TGIS: Model available at /mnt/models<br/>TGIS auto-loads model
